for a start</i>

300
00:21:26,494 --> 00:21:30,707
<i>If this is where the monarchy
is headed, count me out</i>

301
00:21:30,915 --> 00:21:33,334
<i>Out of service
Out of Africa</i>

302
00:21:33,501 --> 00:21:35,670
<i>I wouldn't hang about</i>

303
