329
00:22:55,792 --> 00:22:59,963
<i>Oh, I just can't wait
to be king</i>

330
00:23:00,046 --> 00:23:01,089
Simba!

331
00:23:01,172 --> 00:23:05,260
<i>He just can't wait to be king</i>

332
00:23:05,552 --> 00:23:08,471
<i>Oh, I just can't wait</i>

333
00:23:08,638 --> 00:23:11,099
