You know what this means?

362
00:24:43,691 --> 00:24:45,068
It means we can go home.

363
00:24:45,234 --> 00:24:48,404
It means they won't
treat us like cubs anymore.

364
00:25:37,537 --> 00:25:39,831
Simba, get down!
It could be dangerous.

365
00:25:39,997 --> 00:25:41,332
Danger?

366
00:25:41,416 --> 00:25:44,669
I laugh in the face of danger.

367
00:25:47,839 --> 00:25:48,923
Cool!

368
00:25:49,006 --> 00:25:51,467
You hear that, Nala?

369
00:25:51,968 --> 00:25:53,594
Simba, come on!

370
00:25:53,761 --> 00:25:55,388
You've proved
how brave you are.

371
00:25:55,555 --> 00:25:56,681
Now the sun is going down,

372
00:25:56,764 --> 00:25:58,725
I'm not just
gonna sit here and...

