381
00:26:39,182 --> 00:26:40,725
We have talked
about this before.

382
00:26:40,892 --> 00:26:42,018
I come in alone.

383
00:26:42,185 --> 00:26:44,437
I'm the lead distraction
so everyone can circle.

384
00:26:44,604 --> 00:26:46,814
Okay, okay. Sorry.

385
00:26:46,981 --> 00:26:48,608
Don't be sorry.
Just do it.

386
00:26:48,775 --> 00:26:51,986
Now, this is a meal
