398
00:27:29,398 --> 00:27:31,859
They made a mistake,
a horrible mistake!

399
00:27:32,026 --> 00:27:35,947
But if you do this, you will
start a war with Mufasa!

400
00:27:36,113 --> 00:27:37,782
Hyenas and lions
have been at war

401
00:27:37,865 --> 00:27:39,617
