404
00:27:50,545 --> 00:27:52,547
Don't let them get away!

405
00:28:04,934 --> 00:28:05,935
Come on!

406
00:28:26,914 --> 00:28:28,291
Did you hear that?

407
00:28:28,457 --> 00:28:29,917
The future king!

408
00:28:30,126 --> 00:28:31,544
Oh, don't hurt me!

409
00:28:31,627 --> 00:28:33,337
Do it again!

410
00:29:08,497 --> 00:29:11,042
If you ever come
near my son again...

411
00:29:11,208 --> 00:29:14,211
No, Mufasa. Never.

412
00:29:14,962 --> 00:29:16,047
