you put Nala in danger.

430
00:31:13,622 --> 00:31:16,042
Do you understand
what's at stake?

431
00:31:16,917 --> 00:31:20,629
You jeopardized
the future of our pride.

432
00:31:20,796 --> 00:31:23,883
I just wanted to show you
I could do it.

433
00:31:24,050 --> 00:31:26,010
That I could be brave
like you.

434
00:31:26,177 --> 00:31:28,345
I'm only brave
when I have to be,

435
00:31:28,429 --> 00:31:30,347
when there's no other choice.

436
00:31:30,514 --> 00:31:32,892
But you're not scared
of anything.

437
00:31:33,392 --> 00:31:34,894
