even kings get scared, huh?

441
00:31:46,405 --> 00:31:48,657
More than you could ever know.

442
00:31:48,824 --> 00:31:50,659
- But guess what?
- What?

443
00:31:50,826 --> 00:31:54,497
I think those hyenas
were even scareder.

444
00:31:54,663 --> 00:31:57,541
That's 'cause nobody messes
with your dad.

445
00:31:57,708 --> 00:31:58,876
Come here.

446
00:32:11,847 --> 00:32:12,890
