- Right.

448
00:32:16,143 --> 00:32:18,104
And we'll always
be together...

449
00:32:18,270 --> 00:32:19,814
right?

450
00:32:20,981 --> 00:32:25,653
Simba, let me tell you
something my father told me.

451
00:32:25,820 --> 00:32:27,738
