he will never forget.

476
00:33:56,577 --> 00:33:58,704
Well, you're in luck!
He's right behind ya.

477
00:33:58,871 --> 00:34:00,331
Mufasa?

478
00:34:14,303 --> 00:34:16,263
That's not the king.

479
00:34:18,224 --> 00:34:21,560
You fools have stripped your
land of every living thing.

480
00:34:21,727 --> 00:34:24,730
And yet I send
two little cubs your way...

481
00:34:24,897 --> 00:34:26,398
and they come back alive.

482
00:34:26,732 --> 00:34:29,318
