undoubtedly presage</i>

501
00:35:35,926 --> 00:35:38,887
<i>The need for a dif'rent dream</i>

502
00:35:39,972 --> 00:35:43,017
<i>Yes, leonine times
are a-changing</i>

503
00:35:44,018 --> 00:35:47,229
<i>Which means
that hyenas must too</i>

504
00:35:48,230 --> 00:35:52,192
