and wide-ranging</i>

505
00:35:52,484 --> 00:35:55,195
<i>And even encompasses you</i>

506
00:35:56,613 --> 00:35:59,992
<i>So prepare
for the coup of the century</i>

507
00:36:00,951 --> 00:36:04,038
<i>Prepare for the murkiest scam</i>

508
00:36:05,039 --> 00:36:06,832
<i>Meticulous planning</i>

509
00:36:06,999 --> 00:36:08,917
<i>Tenacity spanning</i>

510
00:36:09,084 --> 00:36:12,588
<i>Decades of denial
ls simply why I'll</i>

