<i>I'm a long way from the start
But further from the end</i>

1519
01:51:30,268 --> 01:51:35,106
<i>Oh, oh, it's never too late</i>

1520
01:51:36,816 --> 01:51:38,693
<i>It's never too late</i>

1521
01:51:40,152 --> 01:51:42,196
<i>Oh, never too late</i>

1522
01:51:44,115 --> 01:51:46,117
<i>Oh, it's never too late</i>

1523
